# Bare patterns are anchored to the build context root (the repo root), so they
# only match e.g. ./.next — NOT packages/ui/.next. The build context for both
# Dockerfiles is the repo root, so the **/-prefixed variants below are what
# actually keep nested workspace artifacts (e.g. the 329MB packages/ui/.next)
# out of the context and stop the broad `COPY packages/ui/ ...` from busting the
# layer cache. next build / npm ci regenerate these inside the image regardless.
node_modules
.next
dist
out
build
.turbo
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/out
**/build
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
.git
.claude
.rondoflow
coverage
.nyc_output
*.md
!README.md
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
